  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients one month after myocardial infarction

          -  Older 18 years

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Age above 75 years,

          -  Inability to exercise,

          -  Hemodinamically significant valvular disease,

          -  Moderate to severe chronic lung disease (vital capacity and/or forced expiratory
             volume in 1 s &lt;80% of age-dependent predicted value),

          -  Atrial fibrillation

          -  Exercise induced myocardial ischemia

          -  Anaemia (haemoglobin &lt;12 g/dl).
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
